{"title":"让爱回家（歌词）","authors":["康宁"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":5,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"让爱回家（歌词）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"康宁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥望夜空那弯弯的月牙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月光洗去身上的疲乏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是我无情不把你牵挂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命的重托不能有余暇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就让我们默默地祈祷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弯弯的月牙将会又圆又大。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让爱回家——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陪伴我亲爱的爸妈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让爱回家——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲吻我疼爱的娇儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让爱回家——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依偎我心爱的他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让爱回家——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让爱回到每一个家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着东方那红红的朝霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝霞染满我身上的白褂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白褂上曾经佩带着鲜花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜花它诉说着真情无价。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就让我们默默地奉献，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红红的朝霞正把爱心播撒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让爱回家——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陪伴你亲爱的爸妈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让爱回家——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲吻你疼爱的娇儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让爱回家——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依偎你心爱的他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让爱回家——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让爱回到每一个家"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}